comment: Horford (ATL) does not dislodge Sullinger (BOS) on the rebound.
Schroder (ATL) makes contact with the airborne shooter Thomas (BOS) on his jump shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor was overturned and officials determined that the shot attempt by Thomas (BOS) was a 3-point shot.
Korver (ATL) sets the screen on Johnson (BOS) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor was overturned and officials determined that the shot attempt by Horford (ATL) was a 2-point shot.
Millsap (ATL) makes incidental contact with Jerebko's (BOS) arm after he finishes his follow through.
Jerebko (BOS) is in a legal guarding position as he defends Millsap's (ATL) shot attempt.
Crowder (BOS) makes contact with Millsap's (ATL) arm that affects his ability to gain possession of the loose ball.

After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor was overturned and officials determined that Korver (ATL) did not touch the ball on the Boston inbound before it went OOB and Atlanta obtained possession.
Bradley (BOS) commits a take foul on Schroder (ATL).
[Observable in enhanced video] Turner (BOS) moves his pivot foot.
Horford (ATL) makes contact to Turner's (BOS) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Olynyk (BOS) commits a take foul on Millsap (ATL).
